{"tid":2232419,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"原神 外媒評分出爐 : 驚艷迷人","createTime":"2020-10-06T11:01:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-07T08:47:22.000Z","uid":25345,"like":3,"dislike":63,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"0a45a890b506ee30d05210db63d0d2222111cca2","tid":2232419,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:01:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://image.playgame.wiki/2020/10/04/0e3a88fa82/16889c6d581c509d3d513b8aa8dcc8f8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage.playgame.wiki%2F2020%2F10%2F04%2F0e3a88fa82%2F16889c6d581c509d3d513b8aa8dcc8f8.jpg&h=caaefded&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《原神》首個外媒評分出爐：GameInformer 9.25分<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《原神》國外首個媒體評分出爐，本作獲得知名媒體GameInformer 9.25分評價。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n評價總結：9.25分<br />\n<br />\n《原神》呈現了一個迷人的世界。<br />\n<br />\n（設計）概念<br />\n<br />\n探索一個大型的幻想世界，同時建立多姿多彩的角色<br />\n<br />\n畫面<br />\n<br />\n畫面迷人，經常讓我迷失在風景如畫的風光中<br />\n<br />\n聲效<br />\n<br />\n不管是靜坐在一個小池塘旁還是和Boss展開生死對決，激動人心的配樂總能準確捕捉你的感覺<br />\n<br />\n遊戲性<br />\n<br />\n《原神》將其系統慢慢而簡明扼要地提供給玩家，在頭10個小時內就能看到關鍵的機制和特色<br />\n<br />\n與類型<br />\n<br />\n《原神》非常完美地融合了探索，發現，戰鬥和自定義，值得你的關注，儘管存在掠奪性的盈利模式<br />\n<br />\n重玩性<br />\n<br />\n高"},{"pid":"a7f10c3a3177ab66e1a5021fa03dac89ecbd0c65","tid":2232419,"uid":109923,"like":36,"dislike":0,"score":36,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-06T11:10:44.000Z","msg":"GameInformer同ign一樣業界權威<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PQFanrm.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPQFanrm.jpg&h=b238a0a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B8X0KEH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB8X0KEH.jpg&h=b229bd6f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"95c1943bceb3464a05fb4d56130823fc246048f7","tid":2232419,"uid":37666,"li